    Table Plus ÏÑ§Ïπò

    Ubuntu 20.04
# Add TablePlus gpg key
wget -qO - http://deb.tableplus.com/apt.tableplus.com.gpg.key | sudo apt-key add -

# Add TablePlus repo

# Install
sudo apt update
sudo apt install tableplus
